column5: I am going to Lac Suel the last week in Aug. Any suggestions????? Will be staying at Deer Path Lodge

Not sure where that place is, but you could fish anywhere from the 'Lost Lake' area on West towards Websters Bay (including the big bay), fishing windy points, rock piles, drop offs. You could also fish anywhere to the East including Kiwatin and Italian Bays on up into Deception Bay....pretty much anywhere in between holds eyes... Good luck.
Have fished the area for 25 years the last week in July. If interested I will give you our fishing report when we get back. Let me know Jimmy
Jimmy, Please do e-mail me the report when you get back. much appreciated [email protected]

My place is about 5 miles up the road from hudson lost lake boat launch. i usually dont fish lost but put in a pelican or deception to get to crooked or manitou rapids. let me know if you find anything on lost. i would be interested to hear [email protected]
